{
  "spec": {
    "title": "CSS Conditional Rules Module Level 5",
    "url": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/"
  },
  "algorithms": [
    {
      "name": "evaluate a <style-range>",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#evaluate-a-style-range",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"evaluate-a-style-range\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">evaluate a <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#typedef-style-range\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-style-range③\">&lt;style-range&gt;</a></dfn>,\n\t\tthe following steps needs to be performed:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#typedef-style-range-value\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-style-range-value⑨\">&lt;style-range-value&gt;</a> is a <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css-variables-1/#typedef-custom-property-name\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-custom-property-name②\">&lt;custom-property-name&gt;</a>,\nit needs to be substituted\nas if the <span class=\"production\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-custom-property-name③\">&lt;custom-property-name&gt;</span> was wrapped inside a <a class=\"css\" data-link-type=\"maybe\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css-variables-1/#funcdef-var\" id=\"ref-for-funcdef-var①\">var()</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Substitute <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css-values-5/#arbitrary-substitution-function\" id=\"ref-for-arbitrary-substitution-function\">arbitrary substitution function</a> within <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#typedef-style-range-value\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-style-range-value①⓪\">&lt;style-range-value&gt;</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Parse <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#typedef-style-range-value\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-style-range-value①①\">&lt;style-range-value&gt;</a> to\n<a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css-values-4/#number-value\" id=\"ref-for-number-value\">&lt;number&gt;</a>, <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css-values-4/#percentage-value\" id=\"ref-for-percentage-value\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a>, <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css-values-4/#length-value\" id=\"ref-for-length-value④\" title=\"Expands to: advance measure | cap | ch | cm | dvb | dvh | dvi | dvmax | dvmin | dvw | em | ex | ic | in | lh | lvb | lvh | lvi | lvmax | lvmin | lvw | mm | pc | pt | px | rcap | rch | rem | rex | ric | rlh | svb | svh | svi | svmax | svmin | svw | vb | vh | vi | vmax | vmin | vw\">&lt;length&gt;</a>, <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css-values-4/#angle-value\" id=\"ref-for-angle-value\" title=\"Expands to: deg | grad | rad | turn\">&lt;angle&gt;</a>, <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css-values-4/#time-value\" id=\"ref-for-time-value\" title=\"Expands to: ms | s\">&lt;time&gt;</a>, <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css-values-4/#frequency-value\" id=\"ref-for-frequency-value\">&lt;frequency&gt;</a> or <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css-values-4/#resolution-value\" id=\"ref-for-resolution-value\" title=\"Expands to: dpcm | dpi | dppx | x\">&lt;resolution&gt;</a>.\nIf this cannot be done, evaluate to false.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If each <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#typedef-style-range-value\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-style-range-value①②\">&lt;style-range-value&gt;</a> from the range have the same type,\ncompute each and evaluate the comparison;\na unitless zero must be treated as being a zero-<a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css-values-4/#length-value\" id=\"ref-for-length-value⑤\" title=\"Expands to: advance measure | cap | ch | cm | dvb | dvh | dvi | dvmax | dvmin | dvw | em | ex | ic | in | lh | lvb | lvh | lvi | lvmax | lvmin | lvw | mm | pc | pt | px | rcap | rch | rem | rex | ric | rlh | svb | svh | svi | svmax | svmin | svw | vb | vh | vi | vmax | vmin | vw\">&lt;length&gt;</a> when compared against a <span class=\"production\" id=\"ref-for-length-value⑥\">&lt;length&gt;</span> .</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Otherwise evaluate to false.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "CSSContainerRule.conditionText",
      "html": "",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>conditions</var> be the result of getting the <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#dom-csscontainerrule-conditions\" id=\"ref-for-dom-csscontainerrule-conditions\">conditions</a></code> attribute.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>first</var> be <code class=\"highlight\">true</code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>result</var> be the empty string.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-iterate\" id=\"ref-for-list-iterate\">For each</a> <var>condition</var> in <var>conditions</var>:",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>first</var> is <code class=\"highlight\">false</code>, append <code class=\"highlight\"><c- s=\"\">\", \"</c-></code> to <var>result</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>first</var> to <code class=\"highlight\">false</code>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "If <var>condition</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#dom-csscontainercondition-name\" id=\"ref-for-dom-csscontainercondition-name\">name</a></code> is not empty:",
              "rationale": "append",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "html": "<p>Append <var>condition</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#dom-csscontainercondition-name\" id=\"ref-for-dom-csscontainercondition-name①\">name</a></code> to <var>result</var>.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "html": "<p>If <var>condition</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#dom-csscontainercondition-query\" id=\"ref-for-dom-csscontainercondition-query\">query</a></code> is not empty,\n append a single space to <var>result</var>.</p>"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Append <var>condition</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#dom-csscontainercondition-query\" id=\"ref-for-dom-csscontainercondition-query①\">query</a></code> to <var>result</var>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <var>result</var></p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "CSSContainerRule.containerName",
      "html": "",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>conditions</var> be the result of getting the <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#dom-csscontainerrule-conditions\" id=\"ref-for-dom-csscontainerrule-conditions①\">conditions</a></code> attribute.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "If the length of <var>conditions</var> is 1:",
          "rationale": "return",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Return the only <var>conditions</var> item’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#dom-csscontainercondition-name\" id=\"ref-for-dom-csscontainercondition-name②\">name</a></code>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>return <code class=\"highlight\"><c- s=\"\">\"\"</c-></code>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "CSSContainerRule.containerQuery",
      "html": "",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>conditions</var> be the result of getting the <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#dom-csscontainerrule-conditions\" id=\"ref-for-dom-csscontainerrule-conditions②\">conditions</a></code> attribute.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "If the length of <var>conditions</var> is 1:",
          "rationale": "return",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Return the only <var>conditions</var> item’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#dom-csscontainercondition-query\" id=\"ref-for-dom-csscontainercondition-query②\">query</a></code>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <code class=\"highlight\"><c- s=\"\">\"\"</c-></code>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "CSSContainerRule.conditions",
      "html": "",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>result</var> be an empty <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list\" id=\"ref-for-list\">list</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-iterate\" id=\"ref-for-list-iterate①\">For each</a> <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#typedef-container-condition\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-container-condition⑦\">&lt;container-condition&gt;</a> <var>condition</var> specified in the rule:",
          "rationale": "let",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>dict</var> be a new <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#dictdef-csscontainercondition\" id=\"ref-for-dictdef-csscontainercondition①\">CSSContainerCondition</a></code> with\n <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#dom-csscontainercondition-name\" id=\"ref-for-dom-csscontainercondition-name③\">name</a></code> set to the\n <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/cssom-1/#serialize-an-identifier\" id=\"ref-for-serialize-an-identifier\">serialized</a> <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#typedef-container-name\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-container-name④\">&lt;container-name&gt;</a>\n of <var>condition</var> if specified, or <code class=\"highlight\"><c- s=\"\">\"\"</c-></code> otherwise,\n and <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#dom-csscontainercondition-query\" id=\"ref-for-dom-csscontainercondition-query③\">query</a></code> set to the\n <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-5/#typedef-container-query\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-container-query⑦\">&lt;container-query&gt;</a> specified in <var>condition</var>\n without any logical simplifications,\n so that the returned query will evaluate to the same result\n as the specified query\n in any conformant implementation of this specification\n (including implementations that implement future extensions\n allowed by the <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/mediaqueries-5/#typedef-general-enclosed\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-general-enclosed④\">&lt;general-enclosed&gt;</a> extensibility mechanism in this specification).\n In other words,\n token stream simplifications are allowed\n (such as reducing whitespace to a single space\n or omitting it in cases where it is known to be optional),\n but logical simplifications (such as removal of unneeded parentheses,\n or simplification based on evaluating results) are not allowed.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-append\" id=\"ref-for-list-append\">Append</a> <var>dict</var> to <var>result</var>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <var>result</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}